**Key Responsibilities:**

- Delivering sales of relevant brands to assigned wholesale customers/accounts
- Managing assigned account for the wholesale business
- Selling in future ranges and delivering brand strategies, product stories, and key commercial objectives for each season to accounts
- Managing the order book continuously and selling available free stock to drive positive stock management
- Monitoring and reporting on sell-through of all wholesale accounts
- Ensuring efficient processes for sales, finance, marketing, operations, and customer experience
- Delivering consistent communication with key personnel at all accounts
- Supporting the negotiation, completion and overall delivery of Accent Trading Terms and key commercial objectives
- Staying relevant with the brand being sold, the customer being serviced, and overall marketplace
- Being diligent on all costs and acting within budget and expectations for travel, samples, marketing, entertainment, ensuring profitability for the brand and wholesale business

**Skills:**

- Sales/Account Management
- Retail, apparel & footwear product knowledge
- Sufficient business skills
- Negotiation skills
- Communication skills
- Proficiency in sales and marketing tools
- Understanding of finance and operations within retail industry

